name: Roberto Portales \ RJPortales
description:
Info about the person:

Roberto Portales is an actor, fitness trainer, fitness model, and captain of the West Point Army.

Note about the model:

This model was requested from here. It was trained on a dataset of 67 images, I always try to add more images if their quality is good, and this model also shows good results in the DeepFace tests. You can find the dataset (txt and img) of this model here.

It's too hot on Civitai, feel free to get me a drink!
